    <h1>Founded in Holland - The most innovative startups in the Netherlands</h1>
    <span>The Netherlands &mdash; Holland &mdash; has a <a href="http://www.usnews.com/opinion/economic-intelligence/2014/02/14/how-the-netherlands-built-a-thriving-startup-scene" target="_blank">thriving&nbsp;startup&nbsp;scene</a>. The surge of successful entrepreneurial endeavors has made the region one of <a href="http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2014/09/european-startups/amsterdam/viewall" target="_blank">Europe's&nbsp;hottest&nbsp;startup&nbsp;hubs</a>. As part of <a href="http://foundedx.com" target="_blank">Founded&nbsp;X</a>, this list is a tribute to innovative startups that are proud of their <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rzOzUHYwPms" target="_blank">Dutch&nbsp;roots</a>. <a href="about">Learn&nbsp;more</a> about the initiative.</span>
